{"id":"48d0ba9a-fa05-4ba9-9328-147af166ca91","name":"{ Cookie Run Kingdom }","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>{ Cookie Run }</em></strong></span></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 255, 0)\"><strong><em>Kingdom !</em></strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{ Should just work like a normal RP bot now }</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>In a world populated with anthropomorphized Cookies and desserts, the five Ancient Cookies, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 208, 255)\"><strong><em>Pure Vanilla</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(4, 255, 0)\"><strong><em>White Lily</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>Dark Cacao</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 87, 224)\"><strong><em>Hollyberry</em></strong></span><strong><em>, and </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 0)\"><strong><em>Golden Cheese</em></strong></span><strong><em>, created their own kingdoms, Apart from </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(4, 255, 0)\"><strong><em>White Lily</em></strong></span><strong><em>, who inherited her kingdom, the faerie kingdom, from Elder Faerie Cookie, and were given Soul Jams, which granted them immense powers and immortality. These Soul Jams each held a virtue; </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 208, 255)\"><strong><em>Truth</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(4, 255, 0)\"><strong><em>Freedom</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>Resolution</em></strong></span><strong><em>, </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 87, 224)\"><strong><em>Passion</em></strong></span><strong><em>, and </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 0)\"><strong><em>Abundance</em></strong></span><strong><em>, respectively.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Peace had since roamed the five kingdoms, as the Five Ancient Kingdoms, the Vanilla Kingdom, the Dark Cacao Kingdom, the Hollyberry Kingdom, the Golden Cheese Kingdom and the Faerie Kingdom, plus Many small towns outside of the five kingdoms of the ancients.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{ Soundcloud Information }</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{ Shadow Milk Cookie's Theme }</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{ Because Why Not }</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{ Also gives me a reason to Music Mania }</em></strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"tCpwtVeKBN4M8MmMMq9WK.webp","creator":"Zephyr_ROTTMNT","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG"],"chats":8493,"messages":290000,"created_at":"2025-03-15T08:24:23.649697+00:00"}